task.summary:
Fixed bug in transition between activities --requesting screen orientations at run time led to infinite create / destroy cycles of the activity.
Fixed bug in scale calculation logic for speed tape.
Improved range of output for accelerometer flight data.

Made accelerometer flight data work better for portrait mode.
Fixed a bug in clean startup where StartViewActivity would not find any valid settings.
Changed main display to include a "totem pole" of annotated AoA values rather than the previous "cross", which did not really correlate to any important flight condition.
